sentences.english: The tariff will be calculated from the date goods entered into China.
sentences.chinese: 計徵稅款的期限自貨物放行之日起計算。

sentences.english: Monitor and control serial production quality and release technical changes in QDA system.
sentences.chinese: 監視和控制序列化生產質量和放行技術變更。

sentences.english: Meet the requirements and audit staff products can only be released after the signing.
sentences.chinese: 符合要求並有審覈人員簽字後方可將產品放行。

sentences.english: I'll sign them out and gua rant ee their good behavior.
sentences.chinese: 我給他們簽字放行，保證他們行爲端正。

sentences.english: Receiving, sampling, testing, release procedures have been established to fulfill this Subpart.
sentences.chinese: 建立接收，取樣，測試與放行程序。

sentences.english: The Customs office shall let them pass after checking the Certificate of Approval for Special Articles issued by the health and quarantine organ.
sentences.chinese: 海關憑衛生檢疫機關簽發的特殊物品審批單放行。

sentences.english: Endorsement of aircraft types means the holder is qualified to issue maintenance release for such aircraft at the date of endorsement.
sentences.chinese: 持照人在機型簽署之日起具有對該機型的放行資格。

sentences.english: And cover three types of inspections in the bill of lading release white chapter.
sentences.chinese: 並在白色提貨單上蓋三檢放行章。

sentences.english: If it do need chemical test, the goods can be released after the customs get a sample.
sentences.chinese: 確需進行化驗的，海關抽樣後，貨物可先予放行。

sentences.english: The custom released the goods against payment of a fine.
sentences.chinese: 在付完罰款後海關放行貨物。

sentences.english: Dissolution data on split tablet portions should meet finished-product release requirements.
sentences.chinese: 刻痕片劑部分的溶出度數據應該滿足製劑放行要求。

sentences.english: The man explained that he was just waiting for “the green light.
sentences.chinese: 那人解釋說他只是在等待“綠燈放行”。

sentences.english: The trouble is that La Blaugrana have imposed a minimum release fee of 90 million.
sentences.chinese: 麻煩的是，巴薩實行的最低放行費爲9千萬英鎊。

sentences.english: Filled cylinders should be held in quarantine until released by the qualified person.
sentences.chinese: 充好的氣瓶應保持在待檢區，直至有資格的人員放行。

sentences.english: Endorsement of item rating means the holder is qualified to issue maintenance release for such item at the date of endorsement.
sentences.chinese: 持照人在項目簽署之日起具有對該項目的放行資格。
